Hi Richard and Shane,

There is no redirect currently in place for that URL. You can have a look at a redirect checker such as this: https://www.whatsmydns.net/redirect-checker?q=https%3A%2F%2Ftrueline.net.au%2Flocations%2Fmelbourne%2F

It shows a 200 message, which means the URL is loading as intended and that there is no redirect associated with this URL.

Your machine has likely cached an old redirect at some point. Please clear your browser cache, try in incognito as mentioned and even closing down your internet browser and restarting your machine can flush it out. Another trick is to access the page from a different internet connection. For example, turn your phone off WiFi and use your 4g/mobile data to access the site.

Let me know how that goes.

Thanks
